	  	<show chara="weltNormalClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>					
			<speak chara="teslaNoFace">这家伙把自己反锁在卧室里发呆，害得我还以为他要闹自杀呢。</speak>
			<show chara="teslaEmbarraClose" position="center" opacity="0.7"/>
